data.description: $25,000 SELLER PAID FINANCING CREDIT!!!! Your dream oasis 5.83 acres, and yes horses are welcome (up to 4) Elkhorn Ranch offers upscale country living, with a commute of 10 minutes to town! DOUGLAS COUNTY SCHOOLS! Save hundreds on water bills with your own private well! Brand new roof (class 4 IR shingles), gutters, exterior paint, refinished wood floors and more! Amazing opportunity to build up to 2500 sq ft outbuilding on the South side of the home! Bring your RVs, boats and toys! Dream come true! Wildlife, horseback riding, Colorado sunsets! Step outside onto the covered deck, where you can take in the sights and sounds of nature. The expansive backyard is your tranquil getaway, paved patio, built in stone fireplace, fenced in landscaped yard for your furry friends. Now for the inside of the home, starting with the oversized garage - incredible storage space, asphalt driveway with lots of room for parking. Stepping in the front door, you'll find an open floor plan living with views of your property from every window. Main floor guest quarters privately located at the front of the home. Kitchen meant for entertaining and hosting, walk in pantry, large island, breakfast nook, expansive great room with fireplace. Upstairs is no less breathtaking, let's start with the primary and that walk in closet!!! 5 piece en suite bathroom with 2 separate vanities, soaking tub, walk in shower. 2 secondary bedrooms with a private entry to their own full jack and jill bathroom, each with their own sink and vanity space. Bonus loft space for a cozy movie night, can easily be converted into 5th bedroom. Conveniently located, this residence offers the best of both worlds – the tranquility of country living with easy access to urban amenities. Your own irrigation well, waiting to be activated. Massive savings and enjoy the benefits, especially if you have horses or other animals and outdoor irrigation. https://youtu.be/9yBllpQuYCY?si=jITeHtTC2hQne586 for video tour!
